  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Types of apartments </strong></p>
<p><strong>Studio (B3) 22m² - sleeps 2-3</strong> Living room with single sofa bed, pull-out bed and pull-down bed.</p>
<p><strong>Studio &amp; cabin (C4) 21m² - sleeps 2-4</strong> Living room with single sofa bed and pull-out bed, cabin room with bunk beds.</p>
<p><strong>2-room Apartment (E4) 25m² - sleeps 2-4</strong> Living room with single sofa bed and pull-out bed and double bed on mezzanine or in separate bedroom.</p>
<p><strong>2-room Apartment (F6) 32m²- sleeps 4-6</strong> Living room with single sofa bed and pull-out bed, double bedroom and cabin room with bunk beds.</p>
<p>All apartments have kitchenette with hotplates, oven, fridge and dishwasher, bathroom, satellite TV (pay locally €41 per week) and balcony.</p>
<p><strong>Included</strong> Bed linen</p>
<p><strong>Local Expenses</strong> Refundable deposit €250 (credit card). Towels €7.50 per set (optional) Resort Taxes.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
